Package com.phasmidsoftware.dsaipg.adt.threesum

Class Pair

java.lang.Object
com.phasmidsoftware.dsaipg.adt.threesum.Pair
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Pair>
public class Pair extends Object implements Comparable<Pair>
The Pair class represents an immutable pair of integers and provides utility methods for comparison, hashing, and summation. This class implements the Comparable<Pair> interface to support natural ordering.
